{"tid":174844,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一件自己做過既衰野","createTime":"2017-03-27T06:17:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-27T06:57:11.000Z","uid":90291,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fea6d70c25d5cf3eaedee9f978cf7f5f9f9c14c1","tid":174844,"uid":90291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T06:17:09.000Z","msg":"話說我前任同現任其實係隔離班既同學<br />\n當時我同前任分手之後成個人頹爆<br />\n現任一直都係我身邊安慰我<br />\n而我同前任關係就一直膠著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後來我同現任一齊左<br />\n至於前任都識左個新男朋友<br />\n<br />\n有次送現任去坐車，發現車站隔離就係前任屋企<br />\n突然之間好掛住佢所以打左比佢<br />\n之後一直keep住有聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n後來女朋友發現左好嬲，問我係咪舊情復燃<br />\n佢話要分手，我仲鬧翻佢轉頭話佢唔信我<br />\n當佢發脾氣走左既時候，我前女友打比我<br />\n然後我果斷去搵前女友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n後來現任搵翻我，我仲要佢道歉我先肯原諒佢。<br />\n<br />\n諗翻覺得自己好仆街，但其實依家都仲有曚住現任同前女友聯絡互flirt<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"293cce77b66d009b7141ba3e29516a3c24044642","tid":174844,"uid":70292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T06:19:34.000Z","msg":"人類就係咁，落到凡間要經生老病死，仲要受七情六慾既折磨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4213ac8cfa4a73c9ebff860bce35439dc4a22e75","tid":174844,"uid":70292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T06:20:22.000Z","msg":"打丁算唔算衰野，如果以道德撚黎講既話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31c57be40cb3fcb236a12806b6ab69968518f4d9","tid":174844,"uid":62822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T06:21:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c413159715c185e947ab41501fd437a508eec073","tid":174844,"uid":93876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T06:31:01.000Z","msg":"知衰仲咁做"},{"pid":"f9f2b272ff82fcf33d6682509929d09aa5548fd7","tid":174844,"uid":793